{"tid":2229559,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港成個社會都噉功利?","createTime":"2020-10-04T13:11:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T13:16:19.000Z","uid":204227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8d202308323be8040cc866531119a93213e37c57","tid":2229559,"uid":204227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T13:11:55.000Z","msg":"唔知大家細個有冇聽過呢啲說話：<br />\n讀書一定要考第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n參加咩比賽都要做冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攞100分就有禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要自己係學習上有好好嘅成績<br />\n就會有獎勵＆可以入大學然後打份好工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係香港，細細個就已經會俾屋企人/親戚/學校/老師等嘅人不停直接/間接噉話俾自己知學習唔係為知識<br />\n而係為咗<span class=\"xx-large\">得到獎勵/搵到份好工</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦大個咗，係各種社交場合下嘅時候<br />\n總係會講到下面嘅話題<br />\n去同對方曬/比較各自嘅：<br />\n學歷GPA/Hons/Intern<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCareer path＆薪酬待遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n車/樓/其他物質<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底點解全部都係圍繞住錢/物質/社經地位上嘅嘢呢樣嘢係咪香港獨有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df765bf330130404e87987d381b04ed1ec26f89","tid":2229559,"uid":204227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T13:16:19.000Z","msg":"諗諗下<br />\n香港嘅老豆老母又係會經常同自己啲同輩朋友<br />\n講自己仔女讀緊乜/翻乜工/幾錢人工<br />\n生個仔/女出嚟係咪就係用嚟同人曬命<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}